reviewText: Buy it, you'll love it.  Love, Love, Love, Love, Love, it.  A must see on all fronts.  Know your God and know the traps of the enemy.

Wow! I can't brag enough about this DVD. EX Ministries did all the research and laid it out in an entertaining, yet scary, DVD presentation. G Craige has all the proof before you and leaves nothing to the imagination. After watching this, I read every label in my food pantry and pitched tons. I had no idea I was poisoning my family! You have no idea what is really going on in the food industry until you watch this. Great DVD!
